1) Write a program to print sum of first n even numbers using while loop

public static void main(String s[]){
        int n=3;
        int sum=0;
        while(n!=0){
            sum+=n*2;
            n--;
        }
        System.out.println(sum );

    }
    
    o/p
    12
    
    
    2) Write a program to print multiplication table of a given number n
    
     public static void main(String s[]){
        int n=2;
        int counter =1;
        while(n!=0){
            System.out.println(n*counter);
            counter++;
            if(counter==11)
                break;

        }

    }
    
    o/p
    2
    4
    6
    8
    10
    12
    14
    16
    18
